n\ln\bigg(1+\frac{4}{\sqrt{n}}\bigg)=2\cdot\sqrt{n}\cdot\dfrac{\ln\bigg(1+2\cdot\frac{2}{\sqrt{n}}\bigg)}{\frac{2}{\sqrt{n}}}.
